name: LiveAdmins JLT
description: Live Chat Service provider in UAE
overview:
At LiveAdmins, we base our solutions upon understanding and defining the value & culture of visitors that appear on a particular website. Our true technology, flexible yet comprehensive approach to developing solutions and veteran experience empowers our unique, business-practical and results-oriented solutions.

Over the years, we have broadened our scope in terms of the type of websites we serve, offering a wide variety of Live Chat solutions across a multitude of industries. We have grown into an international company: LiveAdmins has offices and Web Centers located throughout the globe. We have expanded our network to include service in multiple languages, including Arabic.

LiveAdmins has recently opened its Dubai office. We see great opportunity for our company’s growth in the region and beyond. As digital marketing and internet usage are on the rise in the Middle East, Live Chat will become increasingly apparent in the region.
